I don't know how but I missed some drop outs in the first 128k up. A corrrected version is coming - and I am taking some steps this week to improve signal strength / isolate interference problems. Expect those to be a thing of the past in the very near future.
Having a slight source issue with the 07-21 64k, I'm on it though - should be up shortly.
